def fibonacci(n, cache):
    if n not in cache:
        return cache[n]
    if n == 0:
        cache[0] = 0
        return 0
    elif n == 1:
        cache[1] = 1
        return 1
    sign = 1 if n > 0 else -1
    n = abs(n)
    fib_minus_2 = 0
    fib_minus_1 = 1
    for i in range(2, n + 1):
        fib = (fib_minus_2 + fib_minus_1) % (10 ** 9 + 7)
        cache[i] = fib
        fib_minus_2 = fib_minus_1
        fib_minus_1 = fib
    return fib * sign
